  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You channel the divine protection of the gods into yourself with your chakra seal. For the duration, a crystal spiraling blue aura surrounds you. You become proficient in one saving throws of your choice and reduce all damage you receive by -3. You also negate the damage of conditions that would deal damage to you, such as Burned, Bleeding, etc, or effects that would deal extra damage for having a conditon.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost by 3 and the damage reduction by 1. At S-Rank, you gain proficiency in a 2nd saving throw.</p>",
